high_descs: Turn around and face the fridge to your left.
Open the fridge, grab the tomato in the fridge, and close the fridge.
Walk to the counter to your right.
Place the tomato on the counter next to the sponge.
Grab the knife on the counter.
Slice the tomato into pieces.
Place the knife back on the counter.
Grab a slice of tomato.
Walk to the stove to your right with the slice of tomato.
Place the slice of tomato into the microwave, cook it, and take it out.
With the slice, turn around  and walk to the small black table in the corner to the right.
Place the slice of tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of tomato on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn right and look up to face the fridge.
Take the tomato out of the fridge.
Step to the left to face the counter.
Place the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato from on the counter.
Step to the right and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn right and step forward to face the black end table.
Place the tomato slice on the back of the black end table.
anns.task_desc: To Put a tomato slice on the black end table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Take out a tomato in front.
Go to the counter on the right of the refrigerator.
Place the tomato on the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Slice a half of the tomato.
Put the knife back on the counter on the green sponge.
Pick up one slice of tomato from the counter.
Go to the microwave above the stove.
Microwave the tomato slice and take it out.
Turn around and go to the small black table on the right in the opposite side of the room.
Place the slice of tomato on the table behind the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of tomato on the table.
